<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Pamphleteers_and_activists">Pamphleteers and activists</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Patriot_(American_Revolution)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Edit section: Pamphleteers and activists">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Samuel_Adams" title="Samuel Adams">Samuel Adams</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Alexander_Hamilton" title="Alexander Hamilton">Alexander Hamilton</a></li>
